      "start_time": 34.72,
      "recording_attendee_id": "691c16d7-416b-442f-8f60-0755018a2e91",
      "order_number": 12,
      "text": "Okay. Um We partnered with the company, we're rolling out some google my business. Um We we've learned and everything's trending towards a lot of renters are if they're not on social media, they're not on IOS. Is there searching within maps um to find properties to rent?"
    },
    {
      "id": "2d8dedf2-a79b-4839-b378-344adbcfc30b",
      "recording_id": "7d9756c8-f496-40f7-8125-ecead402275c",
      "end_time": 56.46,
      "start_time": 56.37,
      "recording_attendee_id": "aea6c5ad-a79b-4d7c-a1f3-5c8159f13944",
      "order_number": 13,
      "text": "Okay"
    },
    {
      "id": "2d8dedf2-a79b-4839-b378-344adbcfc30b",
      "recording_id": "7d9756c8-f496-40f7-8125-ecead402275c",
      "end_time": 99.92,
      "start_time": 56.9,
      "recording_attendee_id": "691c16d7-416b-442f-8f60-0755018a2e91",
      "order_number": 14,
      "text": "And so we've partnered a lot of every, every property has a google my business page. So if you were to look up the Corey um or any of your properties online on google, they're they're listed in that area. So let's say I'm in bloomington and I type in apartments for rent in bloomington's. Those will pull the top of the google search on the maps page. A lot of places will update those once a month. Some people pay for services that are once a week. We're rolling out uh per property pricing uh to update daily with different updates and things of"
    },
    {
      "id": "2d8dedf2-a79b-4839-b378-344adbcfc30b",
      "recording_id": "7d9756c8-f496-40f7-8125-ecead402275c",
      "end_time": 119.22,
      "start_time": 99.92,
      "recording_attendee_id": "691c16d7-416b-442f-8f60-0755018a2e91",
      "order_number": 15,
      "text": "that. So just another avenue to get renters eyes on your properties and with with google being, you know, the place and a lot of people are searching, thought I'd reach out, thought we were doing pretty well and um I know we've obviously been talking quite a bit these last couple of months, so I wanted to reach out to you and see what your thoughts were."
    },
    {
      "id": "2d8dedf2-a79b-4839-b378-344adbcfc30b",
      "recording_id": "7d9756c8-f496-40f7-8125-ecead402275c",
